artists.strBiographyEN:
Twins Twins consist of five danish rockers, who in the cold, late months of 2006 began creating foxy rock music together. After releasing a few demos during 2007 - "Fiona" went no 1 on Soundvenue High-5, and "San Sebastián" went no 3 on Det Elektriske Barometer (danish radio chart for alternative music) - the band went touring with Figurines, and in the spring of 2008 they recorded their debut ep "Five Songs" set for release in the fall of 2008.

Twins Twins released one album, "Until Dawn" in 2009, before they disbanded.
